name: UCommonSession_SearchResult
doc: A result object returned from the online system that describes a joinable game session

methods.name: GetDescription
methods.doc: Returns an internal description of the session, not meant to be human readable

methods.name: GetIntSetting
methods.doc: Gets an arbitrary integer setting, bFoundValue will be false if the setting does not exist

methods.name: GetMaxPublicConnections
methods.doc: The maximum number of publicly available connections that could be available, including already filled connections

methods.name: GetNumOpenPrivateConnections
methods.doc: The number of private connections that are available

methods.name: GetNumOpenPublicConnections
methods.doc: The number of publicly available connections that are available

methods.name: GetPingInMs
methods.doc: Ping to the search result, MAX_QUERY_PING is unreachable

methods.name: GetStringSetting
methods.doc: Gets an arbitrary string setting, bFoundValue will be false if the setting does not exist
